<view class="container data-v-22fb23d0"><view class="header data-v-22fb23d0"><text class="title data-v-22fb23d0">DBTI 日常人格测试</text><text class="subtitle data-v-22fb23d0">了解真实的自己</text></view><view class="intro data-v-22fb23d0"><view class="intro-item data-v-22fb23d0"><image class="intro-image data-v-22fb23d0" src="https://bk-minigame.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/images/index-bg.png" mode="aspectFit"></image></view><view class="intro-text data-v-22fb23d0"><text class="intro-title data-v-22fb23d0">什么是 DBTI？</text><text class="intro-content data-v-22fb23d0">DBTI是一套</text><text class="intro-content data-v-22fb23d0">专为当代年轻人设计的「日常发疯人格测试」。</text><text class="intro-content data-v-22fb23d0">它不会告诉你该成为谁，</text><text class="intro-content data-v-22fb23d0">只会精准揭露——</text><text class="intro-content data-v-22fb23d0">你是怎么在生活里一点点破大防的。</text><text class="intro-content data-v-22fb23d0">本测试纯属娱乐，</text><text class="intro-content data-v-22fb23d0">适用于年轻人自嘲、吐槽、发疯和社交玩梗。</text></view></view><view class="start-section data-v-22fb23d0"><text class="start-desc data-v-22fb23d0">完成测试后，你将获得详细的人格分析报告</text><button data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['startTest',['$event']]]]]}}" class="start-btn data-v-22fb23d0" bindtap="__e">开始测试</button></view></view>